McKinley</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Wilson-Gorman_Tariff_Act" title="Wilson-Gorman Tariff Act">1894: Wilson-Gorman</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Dingley_Act" title="Dingley Act">1897: Dingley</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Payne-Aldrich_Tariff_Act" title="Payne-Aldrich Tariff Act">1909: Payne-Aldrich</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Revenue_Act_of_1913" title="Revenue Act of 1913">1913: Underwood</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Emergency_Tariff_of_1921" title="Emergency Tariff of 1921">1921: Emergency</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Fordney-McCumber_Tariff" title="Fordney-McCumber Tariff">1922: Fordney-McCumber</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <strong class="selflink">1930: Smoot-Hawley</strong><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Reciprocal_Tariff_Act" title="Reciprocal Tariff Act">1934: Reciprocal</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/General_Agreement_on_Tariffs_and_Trade" title="General Agreement on Tariffs and Trade">1948: GATT</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Trade_Expansion_Act" title="Trade Expansion Act">1962</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Trade_Act_of_1974" title="Trade Act of 1974">1974/75</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/w/index.php?title=Foreign_Trade_Act&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Foreign Trade Act (page does not exist)">1979</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/w/index.php?title=Trade_and_Tariff_Act&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Trade and Tariff Act (page does not exist)">1984</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Omnibus_Foreign_Trade_and_Competitiveness_Act" title="Omnibus Foreign Trade and Competitiveness Act">1988</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Canada-U.S._Free_Trade_Agreement" title="Canada-U.S. Free Trade Agreement" class="mw-redirect">1989: Canada FT</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/North_American_Free_Trade_Agreement" title="North American Free Trade Agreement">1993: NAFTA</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/World_Trade_Organization" title="World Trade Organization">1994: WTO</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/2002_United_States_steel_tariff" title="2002 United States steel tariff">2002: Steel</a></div>
